From Glenn A Sullivan Subject Re making copy of a Video tape In article , Paul Ilgenfritz writes I think the Go Video dual cassette machines do a direct tape to tape copy which transfers Macrovision to the copy I you can find one of these, it would be worth a try Go Video machines used in HQ mode will copy even the MacroVision Go Video phone number Ask for sales department Since the state of Arizona does not go on Daylight Savings time, we effectively are in Pacific time zone Allen Sullivan Designing various stuff for GO Video